{
  "id": "adv_love_2411_08_02",
  "title": "Episode 8 Part 2",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――三年後"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-koh001.wav",
      "text": "電話越しでごめん。でも改めて\n新人俳優賞の受賞、おめでとう\n優、ずっと狙ってたもんな"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-yu001.wav",
      "text": "ありがとう{user}君\nこれであのゴシップ関連の悪評も\n文句なしにはね除けられたやろな"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-yu002.wav",
      "text": "それに、ここまで来られたんは\n{user}君がずーっと\n支えてくれたからやね"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-koh002.wav",
      "text": "支えられた……のかな\nそうだったらいいんだけど"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-koh003.wav",
      "text": "（お互いの気持ちを確認し合ってから三年\n俺達の交際は今でも続いていた\nけど、直接会えた数はそう多くない）"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-koh004.wav",
      "text": "（ゴシップ騒ぎの火に油を注がないよう\n今でも事務所と小島先輩、そして鈴木以外に\n俺達の関係を知る者はいない）"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-koh005.wav",
      "text": "（今となってはあれも過去の騒ぎだが\n変に掘り返されないよう、パパラッチの目を\n気にしながらの交際だからだった）"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-yu003.wav",
      "text": "こうして電話で他愛ないこと話し合える\n時間も、十分息抜きになってるんよ\nだからそんな卑下せんでも……"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-yu004.wav",
      "text": "ああ、でも{user}君は\nうちのこと好き過ぎて、本当はもっともっと\nうちに甘えたいんよね？"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-koh006.wav",
      "text": "……正直に言えば、そうだよ\nでも、優のこれからのことを考えたら……"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-yu005.wav",
      "text": "…………\n確かにうちも、少し考える時はある\nうちら、このままやっていけるんかな、って"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-yu006.wav",
      "text": "炎上には沈黙を貫くって事務所の方針も\n理解は出来るし、うちもその方がいい思って\n納得したつもりやったけど……"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-yu007.wav",
      "text": "……って、ごめんな！\nせっかくのめでたい報告の日なのに\nなんや弱気になってて……"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-koh007.wav",
      "text": "いや、俺の方こそわがままをごめん\n二人でそうしようって決めたことなのに\n今更だったよね……"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-koh008.wav",
      "text": "（けどこの重い空気が全てを物語っている\n今のうちに手を打たないと、この関係は……\n俺は、どうするべきなんだろうか……）"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-koh009.wav",
      "text": "これからもずっと隠し通していくのが\nやっぱりベストなのかな\nでも、俺も来年には就職だし……"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-yu008.wav",
      "text": "ますます時間に融通効かなくなるな\n仕事次第やろうけど……\nそういえば、結局仕事はどないするん？"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-koh010.wav",
      "text": "そうだなぁ……特にやりたいこともないし\n優と休みを合わせられるように、出来るだけ\n有給が取りやすい……いや、待てよ？"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-koh011.wav",
      "text": "（あるぞ……公表せずともある意味合法的に\n優の側にいられて、支えられる方法！\nあとは、俺にその覚悟があるかどうかだ）"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――二年後"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-koh012.wav",
      "text": "……はい、はい、ありがとうございます！\n今後とも、うちの鈴村優を\nどうぞよろしくお願いいたします！"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-yu009.wav",
      "text": "お願いします\nほな、失礼いたします"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-yu010.wav",
      "text": "ふふっ、大御所タレントさん相手だからって\nガッチガチ過ぎやって。腰の角度九十度で\nお辞儀って、ロボットやんか"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-yu011.wav",
      "text": "うちのマネージャーなんやから\nもうちょっと堂々としててくれへんと……\nうちが舐められてまうで？"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-koh013.wav",
      "text": "大ヒット連発の主演俳優である優を\n舐めるタレントなんて、いる訳ないよ"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-koh014.wav",
      "text": "（俺が覚悟を決めて進んだ道は\n芸能事務所のマネージャー職だった\nそれも、優の所属する事務所のだ）"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-koh015.wav",
      "text": "（彼女のマネージャーになれれば\n誰の目も気にせず彼女を側で支えられる\nその目標を……実現させた）"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-yu012.wav",
      "text": "でも、うちがそこまで上り詰めたのは\n{user}君の手腕でもあるな"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-yu013.wav",
      "text": "愛する優を公私共に支えたいから\nマネージャーやらせて下さい……なんて\n社長面接で熱く語った、って聞いた時は……"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-yu014.wav",
      "text": "ほんまにおもろくて……格好いい思ったわ\nそんなマネージャーのおかげなんよ？\n今のうちがおるんは"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-koh016.wav",
      "text": "今の優ももちろんだけど……\nでも俺は、これからもずっと\nこうして支えていくつもりだよ"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-koh017.wav",
      "text": "しわくちゃのお婆ちゃんになった優が\nどんな芝居を見せてくれるのかも\n今から楽しみだからね"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-yu015.wav",
      "text": "あら……ふふっ\nうちのことやから、いい感じに艶のある\n老婆役で、さらに人気になれるやろな"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-yu016.wav",
      "text": "そのためにも、まだまだ頑張らなあかんね\n{user}君……\nこれからも末永く、よろしくな"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-koh018.wav",
      "text": "（こうして俺は、ますます\n人気俳優街道を駆け上がってく優を\n公私にわたって生涯支え続けた）"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-koh019.wav",
      "text": "（そして……完全に二人きりの時にだけ\n身につけていた俺達の結婚指輪の存在は\n最後まで世間に知られることはなかった）"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-koh020.wav",
      "text": "……もしかしたら……\n今が、別れ時……だったりするのかな"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-yu017.wav",
      "text": "……っ！\n……考えんようにって思ってたけど……\nそう……なんかな"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-yu018.wav",
      "text": "でもうちは……{user}君を\n好きって気持ちを持ったまま別れられるほど\n大人やないんよ……"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-koh021.wav",
      "text": "俺もだよ。けどこのままじゃ\n優に余計なストレスを与えちゃう気がする\nその原因に、この恋愛がなってほしくない"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-yu019.wav",
      "text": "そのせいでお互いを嫌いになってしまう\nぐらいなら、好きって気持ちがあるうちに\n別れた方がいい……ってことか"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-yu020.wav",
      "text": "でも……関係までが終わる訳やない\nこれからもずっと、大切な友達でいてほしい\n……いてくれるよね……？"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-koh022.wav",
      "text": "もちろん\n俺達は、最高のオタク友達だよ"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-koh023.wav",
      "text": "（こうして、俺達の恋は終わりを迎えた\nそれぞれの道を歩みつつ、たまに連絡を取り\n他愛ないオタク話に花を咲かせる）"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-koh024.wav",
      "text": "（そんな関係が数年続くうちに、俺は大学を\n卒業して、地元の高校の教員になった\nそんな、ある日のこと）"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "鈴木",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-suzuki001.wav",
      "text": "おお、やっと来た！\n待ってたぜ{user}！\nこっちこっち！"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "小島叶",
      "iconUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-kan001.wav",
      "text": "ふーん、久しぶりに会ったけど\n元気そうじゃん"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-koh025.wav",
      "text": "お待たせ\nごめん、顧問をしてる部活が長引いちゃって"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-koh026.wav",
      "text": "（その日は母校のメンバーでプチ同窓会を\nしようと言うことで、集まっていた\n当然、その中には……）"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-yu021.wav",
      "text": "ふふっ、すっかり立派な学校の先生やな\n{user}君、イジりやすいし\n漫画アニメに詳しいから、人気ありそう"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-koh027.wav",
      "text": "イジりやすいのは、人気とは違う気がする\n……と、とりあえず乾杯しようか！\n久しぶりの再会に……かんぱ～い！"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-koh028.wav",
      "text": "（バスケ日本代表選手でもある鈴木と\n朝ドラ出演を機に人気役者になった小島先輩\nそして、かつて交際していた優と俺……）"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-koh029.wav",
      "text": "（それぞれの道で活躍する俺達の間に\n今はもう、住む世界の違いなんて感じない\nなぜなら――かけがえのない、友達だから）"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-koh030.wav",
      "text": "……優は、どうしたい？\n俺達のこの関係……続けたいと思う？\n正直もう、ギリギリ限界だと思うんだ……"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-yu022.wav",
      "text": "……っ。なんで……うちに委ねるん？\n{user}君、いつもそうやんな\n優しいけど、自分がないゆうか……"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-koh031.wav",
      "text": "だからって、俺の感情で優を縛れないでしょ\n優はこれからも、俳優としてどんどん\n駆け上がっていく存在で――"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-yu023.wav",
      "text": "俳優としてじゃなくて……！\nなんで……普通の彼女としてのうちを\n見てくれへんの……！？"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-koh032.wav",
      "text": "（結局その電話を最後に、俺達の関係は\n悪化してしまい、別れることになった）"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-koh033.wav",
      "text": "（数年後、俺は大学を卒業し、地元の高校で\n教員をすることになった。当然優とは\nすっかり疎遠で、テレビの向こうの存在だ）"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-koh034.wav",
      "text": "（たまにドラマやバラエティ、CMに\n出ているのを見かけるたび\nモヤッとしたものが胸に広がる）"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-koh035.wav",
      "text": "（それでも……別れて良かったんだと\n言い聞かせ、誤魔化している自分がいた\n……そんな、ある日）"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-yu024.wav",
      "text": "……結婚ですか？"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-yu025.wav",
      "text": "なぜって？"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-yu026.wav",
      "text": "だから私は、これからも芝居に恋をし続けて\n一生を過ごすつもりでいるんです\n……その大切な思い出に誓って……"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-koh036.wav",
      "text": "もしかしてそれって、俺との……？\nそうか……あの時の決断は、優にとって\nそんなにも大きな意味を持っていたのか……"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_02-koh037.wav",
      "text": "なら……俺ももっと、自分の本音を\nさらけ出せば……未来は違ったのかな……\nうぅ……優ぅ……！"
    }
  ]
}